text: Roztoki may refer to the following places in Poland: *Roztoki, Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Roztoki, Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship (north-central Poland) *Roztoki, Subcarpathian Voivodeship (south-east Poland) *Roztoki, Lubusz Voivodeship (west Poland) *Roztoki, West Pomeranian Voivodeship (north-west Poland)
title: Roztoki
